Turkey Plans Gender Equality Course for Teachers, Hurriyet Says

-- B y   S t e v e   B r y a n t
-- 
2011-02-16T06:17:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/turkey-plans-gender-equality-course-for-teachers-hurriyet-says.html
  Turkey  is spending 3.6 million euros
($4.9 million) on gender equality training for teachers and new
textbooks, Hurriyet newspaper reported.  The training will last 30 months and is designed to end
gender discrimination at schools, Hurriyet said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
